- Never write raw utility strings for cards, buttons, or inputs.
  Use the existing components in /components/ui/
- Shared styles (border, radius, shadow, base padding) live in the component definition.
- Layout-specific styles (gap, flex direction, width) go in className props at call site, using cn().
- New reusable patterns get extracted into /components/ui/ immediately, not inlined.
- Follow existing token names in globals.css — don't invent new colors/spacing values.
